>\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好多好多好 minor 嘅野都加劇緊香港嘅醫療問題"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-26T17:03:47.000Z","msg":"完全同意"},{"pid":"065e69fef639f3814ff99cfc4d0a3908bc324f7c","tid":996363,"uid":24227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-26T17:21:35.000Z","msg":"人工照加<br />\n花紅照袋 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65a37c18b4d41b8b75c5762576c547d7fb41f44e","tid":996363,"uid":24227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-26T17:24:00.000Z","msg":"<strong>包括在高峰時期安排老人科醫護在急症室照顧長者及分流</strong><br />\n<br />\n佢實係傻撚咗<br />\n做開老人科點識A&amp;E 嘢呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲要人做分流<br />\n出咗事延誤治療就推出去祭旗呀？"},{"pid":"4b006b105d115390e42015224b943cf7180e5f9e","tid":996363,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-26T18:58:25.000Z","msg":"解決唔到咁你醫管局仲有咩用"},{"pid":"808281cf770ce4dc2d61aeb90454124a995be72c","tid":996363,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3e93e7e69897af53871cb149455f7373f35ce0c1","tid":996363,"uid":180712,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"041114acc12b36255f90973ca5d74b708c6130fd","tid":996363,"uid":114275,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"quote":{"pid":"5f0a52f9d9a9d6b26401b4431bfefb640d77d322","tid":996363,"uid":27008,"like":16,"dislike":3,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-26T09:06:54.000Z","msg":"得淡笑  多左儀器多左病房多左hca  但唔夠醫生護士有乜分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-26T09:38:58.000Z","msg":"多 d 空間做野嘅時候起碼舒服 d<br />\n<br />\n( Infection control 又好 d )<br />\n<br />\n多 d hca 起碼可以盡量將 d manual work 同 paper work 推俾佢地做<br />\n<br />\n( 幫手過床換片tick form 你都 thank god 啦 )<br />\n<br />\n多 d diagnostic tools 起碼可以幫到 triage <br />\n<br />\n( 同埋病人覺得你有掂過佢少 d 怨言 )<br />\n<br />\n係解決唔到人手問題架<br />\n<br />\n但係依家日日都有人想 quit<br />\n<br />\n出緊血 你起碼令同事工作環境好 d 先 減慢 d 流失<br />\n<br />\n之後再搵包血嚟輸<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果我提出到個完美嘅辦法可以直接解決到問題嘅話<br />\n<br />\n我洗喺度痞呀 !"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-26T11:34:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-26T19:00:44.000Z","msg":"即係病房文員？見成日請人"},{"pid":"0e3f0d03f67f762986f332741792460592449821","tid":996363,"uid":31841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-26T19:15:32.000Z","msg":"年年5萬隻新香港人,十年就50萬<br />\n仲未計蝗虫產卵能力極強<br />\n十年出唔出到咁多護士醫生醫院呀"}]}